Superb game awareness from Deepti Sharma to run out Chedean Nation! The ball was tucked away to fine leg, Meghna Singh gets in a relay throw to Deepti Sharma at short fine leg, who catches Nation slow to make her ground, fires at the non-striker's end and it's a direct hit! Replays show Nation is short of her ground and India are one wicket away from the win!
